%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^INTIMIDATE%^RESET%^

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Usage: Passive%^RESET%^

%^RESET%^%^ORANGE%^Some abilities will perform an intimidate check to determine their success. Usually this involves causing the target to be demoralized or shaken. The intimidate check is performed per the following calculation:

DC = Target Level (max 50) + Wisdom bonus

An intimidate roll is made as follows, against the above DC:

Result = 1d20 + influence skill

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^See also: %^RESET%^sunder, disarm, shieldbash, shatter, rush, knockdown, agile maneuvers